<!doctype html><html lang="ko"><head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"><title>업체 등록 신청</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/style.css"><style>.wrap{max-width:860px;margin:30px auto;padding:0 18px}.box{border:1px solid #29324f;border-radius:18px;background:#101525;padding:22px}.form{display:grid;gap:10px}.form input,.form select,.form textarea{height:42px;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid #29324f;background:#070b15;color:#fff;padding:0 12px}.form textarea{height:120px;padding:12px}.form button{height:46px;border:0;border-radius:999px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#ff3fb4,#10d9ff);color:#fff;font-weight:900}</style></head><body><header class="top"><a class="brand" href="/">서비스 디렉터리</a><nav><a href="/mypage">마이페이지</a><a href="/logout">로그아웃</a></nav></header><main class="wrap"><section class="box"><h2>업체 등록 신청</h2><% if(done){%><p>신청이 접수되었습니다. 관리자가 확인 후 업체회원으로 연결합니다.</p><%}else{%><% if(error){%><p style="color:#ff6b6b"><%=error%></p><%}%><form method="post" action="/vendor-apply" enctype="multipart/form-data" class="form"><input name="company_name" placeholder="업체명" required><select name="category"><% settings.categories.forEach(x=>{%><option><%=x%></option><%})%></select><select name="region"><% settings.regions.forEach(x=>{%><option><%=x%></option><%})%></select><input name="phone" placeholder="연락처"><input name="kakao_url" placeholder="카카오톡 링크"><input name="email" placeholder="이메일"><input type="file" name="image" accept="image/*"><textarea name="content" placeholder="업체 소개 / 신청 내용"></textarea><button>신청하기</button></form><%}%></section></main></body></html>